com.trendrr.oss
Class SSLContextBuilder

java.lang.Object
  com.trendrr.oss.SSLContextBuilder

public class SSLContextBuilder
extends java.lang.Object

Builder to get to the SSLContext. To create a self signed server cert: http://www.sslshopper.com/article-most-common-java-keytool-keystore-commands.html keytool -genkey -keyalg RSA -alias selfsigned -keystore keystore.jks -storepass password -validity 1360 -keysize 2048

Author:
Dustin Norlander
